      "@type": "asbval:ScopeDriftAssertion",
      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "The candidate task card describes a MetaMiner-based workflow for lantibiotic identification on S. griseus data, which is entirely absent from the paper.",
        "The paper is about DEREPLICATOR+ (a general natural product dereplication algorithm), not MetaMiner or lantibiotic-specific tools.",
        "The paper demonstrates identification of diverse natural product classes (peptides, polyketides, terpenes, benzenoids, alkaloids, flavonoids) across multiple datasets (Actinomyces, Cyanobacteria, Fungi, Lichen, GNPS), not lantibiotic-specific identification.",
        "The task card references specific genomic data (S. griseus FASTA) and spectral data (MSV000080102) that are not discussed in the paper.",
        "The expected output format and content (MetaMiner TSV with specific columns) do not match DEREPLICATOR+ output descriptions in the paper."
