      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/task_005/scope_drift",
      "@type": "asbval:ScopeDriftAssertion",
      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "The card's research question references 'NPDtools' as a unified pipeline containing Dereplicator, VarQuest, and Dereplicator+. The paper does not present these as a single integrated tool suite; DEREPLICATOR and DEREPLICATOR+ are presented as successive improvements, and VarQuest is mentioned only in passing without evaluation.",
        "The card specifies testing on 'MSV000080102-derived test spectra,' but the paper does not use this specific dataset identifier. The paper uses multiple datasets (SpectraActiSeq, SpectraLibrary, SpectraLichen, SpectraCyan, SpectraGNPS) but MSV000080102 is not explicitly mentioned in the provided passages.",
        "The card expects 'MetaMiner' results in both 'standard mode' and 'blind mode.' MetaMiner is not mentioned in the paper at all, and no such mode-dependent analysis is performed.",
        "The card's expected outputs include results from VarQuest, but the paper does not present VarQuest results or benchmarks\u2014only a single citation indicating it was developed alongside DEREPLICATOR.",
        "The paper focuses on DEREPLICATOR+ as the primary novel contribution and compares it to DEREPLICATOR and earlier variants (DEREPLICATOR-CN, DEREPLICATOR-CN-CO, DEREPLICATOR-G), not to external tools like MetaMiner or VarQuest."
      ],
      "asbval:n_drift_notes": 5,
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "task_005",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "card",
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
      "prov:wasGeneratedAtTime": "2026-06-16T05:51:07.428288+00:00",
      "sepio:credibility_status": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/SEPIO_0000339"
      }
    },
    {
