      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Recently, we introduced DEREPLICATOR for searching spectral datasets against the database of peptidic natural products (PNPs) that include nonribosomal peptides (NRPs), and ribosomally synthesized and post-translationally modified peptides (RiPPs). ... DEREPLICATOR+ enables cross-validation of genome-mining and peptidogenomics/glycogenomics results.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper mentions RiPPs and genome-mining cross-validation but does not describe MetaMiner's BGC identifier module or its specific functionality for scanning FASTA files and extracting precursor peptides. The paper focuses on DEREPLICATOR+ for spectral matching, not genome mining. Metabologenomic workflow is mentioned but not detailed in the passages provided.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-s41467-018-06082-8",
