      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Scan genome assemblies in FASTA format using MetaMiner's BGC identifier module to locate putative biosynthetic gene clusters and extract corresponding precursor peptide sequences for a specified RiPP class (lantibiotic, lassopeptide, cyanobactin, or others). This is the first sta",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
