      "asbval:note": "MetaMiner is not mentioned anywhere in the paper. The paper describes DEREPLICATOR and DEREPLICATOR+, which identify natural products (including RiPPs, polyketides, terpenes, etc.) from mass spectra using chemical structure databases. While the paper does mention genome mining (antiSMASH) and BGC validation in the context of validating DEREPLICATOR+ identifications, there is no tool called 'MetaMiner' described or referenced.",
