      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Here we describe DEREPLICATOR+ algorithm for dereplicating spectra against diverse metabolites... DEREPLICATOR+ improves on the previous approaches for identifying peptidic natural products, and extends them for identification of polyketides, terpenes, benzenoids, alkaloids, flavonoids, and other classes of natural products.",
