    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/false-discovery-rate-interpretation/008",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "DEREPLICATOR+ processes all spectra by retaining only six top intensity peaks in each window of size 50 Da... Given a spectrum, we annotate the nodes in a fragmentation graph... score(M,S) as the number of unique masses in S that annotate a node in the fragmentation graph of M... computing statistical significance of MSMs and evaluating FDR",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms use of centroided spectra (top 6 peaks per 50 Da window), p-values, and FDR computation.",
