      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "DEREPLICATOR+ algorithm that improves on the previous approaches for identifying peptidic natural products, and extends them for identification of polyketides, terpenes, benzenoids, alkaloids, flavonoids, and other classes of natural products",
      "asbval:note": "Paper describes DEREPLICATOR+ (not MetaMiner) for matching spectra against metabolite databases. DEREPLICATOR+ identifies RiPPs (ribosomally synthesized and post-translationally modified peptides) including peptidic natural products, but the paper does not specifically focus on lantibiotics or use the tool 'MetaMiner'. The functional role (spectrum-to-database matching for PTM-containing peptides) is present, but the named tool differs.",
