      "asbval:note": "Paper discusses spectral processing and metadata handling (e.g., precursor mass tolerance, FDR thresholds, instrument types: TOF vs Orbitrap) but does not explicitly address file format validation, centroiding status checking, or format conversion as a standalone skill. The paper assumes spectra are already in usable form for analysis.",
