      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "DEREPLICATOR constructs theoretical spectra of peptide natural products by disconnecting all the bridges and 2-cuts representing amide bonds, and measuring the masses of the connected components.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms DEREPLICATOR matches spectra against databases and uses precursor/fragment mass metadata, but does not explicitly discuss centroiding requirements or validation of spectral preprocessing as a prerequisite.",
