    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/metabologenomic-database-construction/008",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "DEREPLICATOR+ algorithm for dereplicating spectra against diverse metabolites... DEREPLICATOR+ enables high-throughput identification of variants of known natural products by spectral networks.",
      "asbval:note": "The paper describes variant identification and enumeration of modified peptides through spectral matching, but does NOT describe genome-to-database construction. The paper's scope is spectral matching against existing databases (AntiMarin, DNP), not construction of RiPP databases from genomes.",
