      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "Paper does not describe class-specific modification rule application during database construction. DEREPLICATOR+ constructs fragmentation graphs from chemical structures but does not enumerate PTM variants or apply class-specific rules for modification generation.",
