      "asbval:evidence_quote": "DEREPLICATOR constructs theoretical spectra of peptide natural products by disconnecting all the bridges and 2-cuts representing amide bonds, and measuring the masses of the connected components.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms DEREPLICATOR performs spectral database matching and scoring against peptide natural products (including RiPPs). However, the paper does not describe it as specifically scoring 'PTM pattern consistency'\u2014it scores matches based on fragmentation graph annotation and shared peaks. The tool is designed for dereplication of diverse metabolites, not exclusively PTM-pattern recognition.",
