      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms use of LC-MS/MS spectra and integration with genomic data (e.g., BGC mining with antiSMASH). However, the paper does not explicitly state that input must be centroided or list specific format requirements (MGF, mzXML, mzML, mzData). The scope is broader than RiPP identification\u2014it covers diverse metabolite classes.",
