      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms identification of variants of known natural products via spectral networks. However, it does not specifically discuss RiPP families (lantibiotics, lasso peptides) or PTM pattern conservation as a use case. The paper demonstrates variant identification across diverse metabolite classes.",
