    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/ripp-peptide-identification-from-spectra/002",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Recently, we introduced DEREPLICATOR for searching spectral datasets against the database of peptidic natural products (PNPs) that include nonribosomal peptides (NRPs), and ribosomally synthesized and post-translationally modified peptides (RiPPs).",
      "asbval:note": "DEREPLICATOR is confirmed in the paper for matching spectra against PNP/RiPP databases. However, the card describes it as a 'core scoring engine within MetaMiner,' but the paper does not mention MetaMiner or describe DEREPLICATOR as a component of MetaMiner. DEREPLICATOR is presented as a standalone tool, not as part of MetaMiner.",
