    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/spectral-library-matching-ripp/000",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "DEREPLICATOR constructs theoretical spectra of peptide natural products by disconnecting all the bridges and 2-cuts representing amide bonds, and measuring the masses of the connected components. By applying spectral networks, DEREPLICATOR enabled identification of variants of known PNPs. While DEREPLICATOR search of GNPS identified hundreds of peptides and their variants, it is limited to dereplicating PNPs and cannot identify other classes of natural products such as polyketides and terpenes. Here we describe DEREPLICATOR+ algorithm for dereplicating spectra against diverse metabolites.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper describes DEREPLICATOR+ (not MetaMiner) as the core tool for spectral matching. DEREPLICATOR+ is a generalized algorithm that handles RiPPs (ribosomally synthesized and post-translationally modified peptides) as one class among many (peptides, polyketides, terpenes, benzenoids, alkaloids, flavonoids). The card's focus on RiPPs specifically is narrower than the paper's scope. MetaMiner is not mentioned in the provided passages.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-s41467-018-06082-8",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "partial",
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "spectral-library-matching-ripp",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "skill_bundle",
      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Match tandem mass spectra against a post-translationally modified ribosomally synthesized and post-translationally modified peptide (RiPP) structure database to identify known and novel RiPP compounds.",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000361"
      },
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
      "prov:wasGeneratedAtTime": "2026-06-16T06:00:11.970513+00:00",
      "sepio:credibility_status": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/SEPIO_0000339"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/spectral-library-matching-ripp/001",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "MetaMiner is not mentioned anywhere in the provided paper passages. The paper focuses on DEREPLICATOR and DEREPLICATOR+. While the paper mentions genome mining (antiSMASH) and BGC validation, it does not describe a tool called MetaMiner or a metabologenomic pipeline integrating genomic and spectral data in the way described.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-s41467-018-06082-8",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "no",
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "spectral-library-matching-ripp",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "skill_bundle",
      "asbval:target_claim_field": "tools",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "MetaMiner - Metabologenomic pipeline that integrates genomic data with mass spectra; identifies putative BGCs, constructs post-translationally modified RiPP structure databases, and performs spectral matching via Dereplicator",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0007675"
      },
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
      "prov:wasGeneratedAtTime": "2026-06-16T06:00:11.970513+00:00",
      "sepio:credibility_status": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/SEPIO_0000340"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/spectral-library-matching-ripp/002",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Recently, we introduced DEREPLICATOR for searching spectral datasets against the database of peptidic natural products (PNPs) that include nonribosomal peptides (NRPs), and ribosomally synthesized and post-translationally modified peptides (RiPPs). DEREPLICATOR constructs theoretical spectra of peptide natural products by disconnecting all the bridges and 2-cuts representing amide bonds, and measuring the masses of the connected components.",
      "asbval:note": "DEREPLICATOR is confirmed as a database search tool for RiPPs (among other peptidic natural products). The paper explicitly names RiPPs as one of the classes it handles.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-s41467-018-06082-8",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "yes",
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "spectral-library-matching-ripp",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "skill_bundle",
      "asbval:target_claim_field": "tools",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Dereplicator - Core database search engine that matches tandem mass spectra against RiPP structure databases and reports significant identifications with scoring",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000033"
      },
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
      "prov:wasGeneratedAtTime": "2026-06-16T06:00:11.970513+00:00",
      "sepio:credibility_status": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/SEPIO_0000338"
      }
    },
