      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "After assembling the short reads using metaSPAdes and genome mining using antiSMASH, one of the NRPS-PKS gene clusters is assigned as the putative almiramide biosynthetic gene cluster based on the amino acid sequence and the PK genes",
      "asbval:note": "antiSMASH is mentioned in the paper as a genome mining tool used in conjunction with DEREPLICATOR+ analysis, but the paper does not describe MetaMiner accepting antiSMASH output files. The paper uses antiSMASH for BGC identification but does not detail file format handling or integration with MetaMiner (which is not mentioned in the paper).",
