      "asbval:note": "The paper mentions DEREPLICATOR+ availability but does not mention NPDtools, MetaMiner, or the specific binaries (rippquest_ms, dereplicate) claimed in the card. The paper does not describe a toolkit container called NPDtools 2.5.0.",
