      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms RiPP identification capability and mentions that Dereplicator identifies 'nonribosomal peptides (NRPs), and ribosomally synthesized and post-translationally modified peptides (RiPPs)'. However, the paper does not explicitly list supported input formats (MGF, mzXML, mzML, mzData) in the provided passages. Format support is mentioned only in the card's tool descriptions citing MetaMiner documentation, not in the main paper text.",
